title: IRS Transcript Codes And WMR Reference Codes
description: Here's what the IRS Where's My Refund reference codes mean when checking WMR online, or calling the IRS, or using the Refund Status tool. The post IRS Transcript Codes And WMR Reference Codes appeared first on The College Investor.
author: Robert Farrington
